Project description

PyNWB is a Python package for working with NWB files. The PyNWBdocumentation can be found at https://pynwb.readthedocs.io

NWB Format API

PyNWB is a Python package for working with NWB files. It provides a high-level API forefficiently working with Neurodata stored in the NWB format.

Neurodata Without Borders (NWB) is a project to develop aunified data format for cellular-based neurophysiology data, focused on thedynamics of groups of neurons measured under a large range of experimentalconditions.

The NWB team consists of neuroscientists and software developerswho recognize that adoption of a unified data format is an important step towardbreaking down the barriers to data sharing in neuroscience.
